{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, our contributions can be stated as:",
    "• Firstly, CCAM-Person improves the backbone of the YOLOv8x-pose baseline.",
    "We replace the top-level C2F feature extraction block with a Multi-scale Receptive Field (MRF) Module to alleviate the limitations of the model's effective receptive region.",
    "• Secondly, we enhance the feature fusion approach of YOLOv8 by introducing the Multi-path Feature Pyramid Network (MFPN) instead of the original PANet.",
    "This further optimizes the interaction of information between different feature levels."
  ]
}